data.description: ***FHA APPROVED CONDO!!! LOCATION! LOCATION! LOCATION!  The Sumerset Condominium complex is right off the 127th st exit, running alongside I57 expressway on the east side and a Park on the west! This beautiful Townhouse was already very well maintained and cared for by the ONE and ONLY ORIGINAL owners since the unit was built in 1994, but the recent upgrades has modernized it so that today's buyers will appreciate! You will get the feel of a single family home with THREE levels of finished living space, a bathroom on every level and outdoor areas including a deck, a porch and green space. The mechanics (Furnace, AC and HWT) are ALL newer (only 5-10 years old)! Due to the homeowner being disabled, this unit is disability-friendly including an electric chairlift (that will stay with the property). The kitchen has brand new appliances with booklets and warranties. The front-load washer and dryer also stays but are AS IS. The Somerset community is a very nice group of homeowners, mostly LONG-TIME residents. Low taxes,  HoA, and low to NO exterior maintenance makes buying this property a NO brainer!
